title: Commending the participants in the Nassau County Little League upon the occasion of observing Nassau County Little League Baseball Days 2011
fulltext:
LEGISLATIVE  RESOLUTION commending the participants in the Nassau County
Little League upon the occasion of observing Nassau County Little League
Baseball Days 2011

WHEREAS, Little League is a wholesome  sports  activity  for  the  young
people  of  Nassau  County,  Long Island, New York State and our Nation,
involving children, teenagers,  coaches,  parents,  sponsors  and  other
interested  men  and women, helping to build character for young compet-
itors through the lessons of sportsmanship and  competition  learned  on
the ballfield; and
  WHEREAS,  Excellence and success in competitive sports are achieved by
practice, team play and team spirit, nurtured by dedicated coaching  and
parental interest and support; and
  WHEREAS,  This Legislative Body is justly proud to commend the partic-
ipants in the Nassau County Little League upon the occasion of observing
Nassau County Little League Baseball Days 2011; and
  WHEREAS, The coaches of Nassau County Little League Baseball teams are
skilled and inspirational tutors who work  diligently  to  help  develop
character and proficiency in their young players; and
  WHEREAS,  Sports  competition  helps to instill the values of teamwork
and pride in our outstanding athletes who have clearly made  a  contrib-
ution to the excellence of Nassau County Little League Baseball; and
  WHEREAS,  Nassau  County  Little  League  Baseball  has  significantly
contributed to the quality of life of the residents of Nassau County and
Long Island by always encouraging and  promoting  greater  understanding
and  community  pride  among Nassau County and Long Island's many gener-
ations of young, and not so young, citizens; now, therefore, be it
  RESOLVED, That this Legislative Body pause  in  its  deliberations  to
commend  the  Nassau  County  Little League upon observing Nassau County
Little League Baseball Days 2011; and be it further
  RESOLVED, That copies of this Resolution, suitably engrossed, be tran-
smitted to the participants of Nassau County Little League Baseball Days
2011.
